org.hibernate.ogm.query.spi

Interface QueryParsingResult

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MongoDBQueryParsingResult, Neo4jQueryParsingResult

    @Experimental(value="This contract is under active development.")
public interface QueryParsingResult
    Represents the result of parsing a JP-QL query by a QueryParserService implementation. Subsequentially, this will contain all the information required by QueryTranslators which is currently obtained from the existing query parser.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
